creator: Ella Wheeler Wilcox
description:
LibriVox recording of Poems of Cheer by Ella Wheeler Wilcox.
Read in English by Greg Giordano; Bruce Kachuk; Ken Masters; Julia Niedermaier; April Walters; Tina Renee D'Souza; Phil Chenevert; Ezwa; Newgatenovelist; Larry Wilson; Ashley-Grace Vo
This is another volume in Ella Wheeler Wilcox's series. This time, the topic is "Cheer". - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
